column4: anyone know hwat happened to unrar? why is it unrar-free now? it doesn't seem to work the correctly anymore
it should if you have multiverse enabled
probably not if you can't install. Pastebin the spew from ``apt-cache policy unrar && sudo apt-get install unrar''
right, you don't have multiverse enabled.
note how you have edgy-backports enabled for multiverse but not edgy itself.
so add those two multiverse lines to "edgy" instead of "edgy-backports"
